<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="139" type="etymology">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="139">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="139">
A combination of the Latin words: &quot; 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="139">ab</emphasis>
-&quot; + &quot; 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="139">dentatus</emphasis>
&quot;, referring to the surstylus with a line discontinuous of prensisetae.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
